description: This elegant 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home is well-appointed with floor-to-ceiling windows, breathtaking panoramic water views & a private balcony overlooking the Boston Harbor. This thoughtfully-designed home boasts an open-concept floor plan, ample natural sunlight, hardwood oak flooring, luxurious marble baths, spacious closets, high-gloss lacquer cabinets, and quartz countertops. The kitchen is equipped with Wolf, Subzero and Miele appliances. This home also includes one deeded parking space in the heated, covered garage under the building. 50 Liberty is a five-star, full-service building in the highly sought-after waterfront district of the Seaport with amenities that define luxury and include: 24-hour concierge, doorman, private waterfront clubroom, expansive state-of-the-art fitness center & more. The Seaport is one of Boston's fastest-growing and most exciting neighborhoods, with a variety of high-end retail and dining options, including Davio's Restaurant coming to 50 Liberty.
